longBusinessSummary: Borana Weaves Limited manufactures and sells textiles in India. It offers unbleached synthetic grey fabrics for fashion, traditional and technical textiles, home d√©cor, interior designing, and other industries; polyester textured yarn; microfilament woven fabrics; and greige polyester woven fabrics for apparel and garments, home textiles, and tent fabrics applications.
